highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Delhi. “Kesariya” is the highest at #14.
“Khaab” by Akhil is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Delhi, up 25 spots at #46.
“Mere Ghar Ram Aaye Hain” by Jubin Nautiyal, Payal Dev, and Manoj Muntashir is the highest new entry on Top Songs Delhi at #78.
“Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Delhi the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
